---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Services & Support"
  description="QA and test automation consulting, AI/LLM evaluation setup, and team training from TestEnigma."
  active="services"
>
  <div class="wrap pagehead">
    <div class="eyebrow">Services &amp; Support</div>
    <h1 class="h-sec">Bring in the person who writes the tests.</h1>
    <p class="sub">Practical help for teams shipping software, and the AI systems inside it.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="wrap sect-tight">
    <div class="svc-grid">
      <div class="svc-card reveal">
        <div class="fc-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 3l7 3v6c0 4.5-3 7.5-7 9-4-1.5-7-4.5-7-9V6z"></path><path d="M9 12.5l2 2 4-4.5"></path></svg></div>
        <h3>QA &amp; Test Automation Consulting</h3>
        <p>Get a working, maintainable test suite in place: from framework choice to CI wiring.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="svc-card reveal" style="--d:.08s">
        <div class="fc-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 3h6"></path><path d="M10 3v6.2L4.8 18a1.6 1.6 0 0 0 1.4 2.4h11.6a1.6 1.6 0 0 0 1.4-2.4L14 9.2V3"></path><path d="M7.5 15h9"></path></svg></div>
        <h3>AI / LLM Evaluation Setup</h3>
        <p>Ground-truth eval harnesses, regression suites, and LLM-as-judge pipelines built for your product.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="svc-card reveal" style="--d:.16s">
        <div class="fc-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="9" cy="8" r="3.2"></circle><path d="M2.8 20a6.2 6.2 0 0 1 12.4 0"></path><circle cx="17.5" cy="8.8" r="2.4"></circle><path d="M15.8 12.2a5 5 0 0 1 5.4 5.4"></path></svg></div>
        <h3>Team Training &amp; Workshops</h3>
        <p>Hands-on sessions that get your team writing tests (and evals) they&#8217;ll actually maintain.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="contact-band reveal">
      <h2>Have a testing problem worth solving?</h2>
      <p>Tell me what&#8217;s breaking, or what you&#8217;re afraid might break.</p>
      <div class="contact-row">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/ajmal-khan-98254871/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Message on LinkedIn</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="mailto:hello@testenigma.com">Email hello@testenigma.com</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
